{"tid":2398533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[台灣大選] 就黎又到台灣九合一大選喇，同大家介紹現時既藍綠形勢","createTime":"2021-02-07T11:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T12:51:55.000Z","uid":52658,"like":41,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a95eeb508eb7dd87a9f5061a99d7edf7c9c06a11","tid":2398533,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:32:18.000Z","msg":"以前陳水扁同馬英九年代<br />\n有所謂既北藍南綠<br />\n但經過左咁多年已經改變左<br />\n都會區慢慢開始綠化 鄉下地方同山區就越黎越藍<br />\n<br />\n岩岩參考左最近兩屆既總統 立委同不分區得票分佈<br />\n<br />\n六都<br />\n<span class=\"violet\">台北市</span><br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">新北市</span><br />\n<span class=\"violet\">桃園市</span><br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">台中市</span><br />\n<span class=\"green\">台南市</span><br />\n<span class=\"green\">高雄市</span><br />\n<br />\n市<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">基隆市</span><br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">嘉義市</span><br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">新竹市</span><br />\n<br />\n縣<br />\n<span class=\"green\">宜蘭縣</span><br />\n<span class=\"blue\">新竹縣</span><br />\n<span class=\"navy\">苗栗縣</span><br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">彰化縣</span><br />\n<span class=\"blue\">南投縣</span><br />\n<span class=\"green\">雲林縣</span><br />\n<span class=\"green\">嘉義縣</span><br />\n<span class=\"green\">屏東縣</span><br />\n<span class=\"blue\">台東縣</span><br />\n<span class=\"navy\">花蓮縣</span><br />\n<span class=\"violet\">澎湖縣</span><br />\n<span class=\"navy\">金門縣</span><br />\n<span class=\"navy\">馬祖縣</span><br />\n<br />\n我深綠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民進黨加油 希望民進黨來年大勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f7abd2deee4a54e1c7c368761a28414c1aa0a0","tid":2398533,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74a26eaecc11592b092a191a4997c9344944bc8","tid":2398533,"uid":37396,"like":